      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 149,
      "message": "Let's use all these fields directly in `leaf` method:\n```\nprivate MerkleTree<V> leaf(V value) {\n    return new MerkleTree<>(valueSerializer, hashAlgorithm, hashForValue.apply(value), Option.of(value), HashMap.empty());\n}\n```\n\nso here we would have \n```\nfinal MerkleTree<V> result = addSubtree(path, leaf(value));\n```",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 3701,
        "name": "Filip Krzywka",
        "display_name": null,
